---
title: "QA Ralph Loop Protocol"
---

flowchart TD
    START(("QA\nDispatched"))

    START --> PREPARE

    PREPARE["📋 PREPARE\nRead plan file, extract success criteria\nRead QA memory: status, regressions, patterns\nRead PM concerns with testable implications\nMap each criterion to a specific task\nCheck git log for recent changes"]

    PREPARE --> TREE

    subgraph CHECK["CHECK"]
        direction TB

        TREE["🌳 Tree Checks -- blocking\nRun test suite\nMachine-verifiable criteria first\nRegression watch list\nStructural assertions"]

        TREE --> VISUAL

        VISUAL["📸 Visual Verification\nScreenshot key pages\nContent visible? Layout intact?\nCompare against visual spec\nCompare against mockup illustration"]

        VISUAL --> AI

        AI["🤖 AI Evaluation\nCriteria machines cannot judge\nEach criterion: PASS or FAIL"]

        AI --> FOREST

        FOREST["🌲 Forest Checks -- advisory\nInterface contract compliance\nPattern consistency across phases\nNaming and domain alignment\nDependency direction\nVisual language compliance"]
    end

    FOREST --> DIAGNOSE

    DIAGNOSE["🔬 DIAGNOSE\nFor each failure:\nWhat failed, expected vs actual\nRoot cause -- WHY is it broken\nWhich task in .goals.json\nKnown pattern from patterns.md?\nImpact on other criteria"]

    DIAGNOSE --> PERSIST

    subgraph PERSIST["PERSIST"]
        direction LR

        MEMORY["Update QA Memory\nstatus.json: trajectory, criteria\nlearnings.txt: new findings\nregressions.md: new or updated\npatterns.md: new or merged"]

        GOALS_UPDATE["Update .goals.json\nTree pass: QA attempt success\nTree fail: QA attempt failure\nTask status: completed or blocked\nForest warnings: notes only"]
    end

    MEMORY --> REPORT
    GOALS_UPDATE --> REPORT

    REPORT{"Verdict?"}

    REPORT -- "PASS" --> PASS_OUT(("All criteria\nmet"))
    REPORT -- "FAIL" --> FAIL_OUT(("Failures listed\nwith fix commands"))

